YnZro9XcVj4.description:
Happy birthday to the literary genius, J.K. Rowling, and her iconic creation, Harry Potter. Enjoy this nice, long video of Harry Potter impressions from the movies and parodies.

Inspired by Brizzy Voices' Harry Potter Impressions (film & fandom) video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Lx1oXIv6Ks8

Catch me again on America's Got Talent. Tuesday, August 1st @ 8/7c on NBC!
